Description: Machines not reporting EPP server due to which new version is not getting installed.
Tried to uninstall the older version in 4ways,
1. Tried with the EPP uninstallation Password but was getting error as invalid Password.
2. Tried to uninstall it from software center using IP uninstall app but it gave error, which is attached to the ticket.
3. Directly tried to install the new version 6.2.2.2 but it also got failed attached error screenshot.
4. Tried with EPP removal script but that also didn't work, it is getting stuck.

Also, when checked the details of machine in EPP it says unlicensed
